title: Maschinenmensch
description: TheMaschinenmensch(lit.'machine-human'inGerman) is a fictionalhumanoid robotfeatured inThea von Harbou's novelMetropolisandFritz Lang'sfilm adaption of the novel. In the film, she is played by German actressBrigitte Helmboth as a robot and in human guise. She was created by the scientistRotwangin dedication to his deceased lover, Hel, though in the novel they have no correlation. Maschinenmensch was one of the first fictional robots ever depicted in cinema, and as a result popularized the concept worldwide.
